# Dotfiles and local setup

## Install dependencies

- Install OH My ZSH from https://ohmyz.sh
- Install dependencies usin brew

      brew install asdf autoconf openssl coreutils fop wxwidgets \
             automake libyaml readline libxslt libtool \
             unixodbc unzip curl sqlite3 ctags neovim starship cmake direnv

## Clone dotfiles

```
git clone --bare https://github.com/alvarolizama/dotfiles.git $HOME/.dotfiles
alias dotfiles='/usr/bin/git --git-dir=$HOME/.dotfiles/ --work-tree=$HOME'
dotfiles checkout

```

## Usage
```
dotfiles status
dotfiles add .vimrc
dotfiles commit -m "Add vimrc"
dotfiles add .bashrc
dotfiles commit -m "Add bashrc"
dotfiles push
```

## Start you own dotfile repo

```
git init --bare $HOME/.dotfiles
alias dotfiles='/usr/bin/git --git-dir=$HOME/.dotfiles/ --work-tree=$HOME
dotfiles config --local status.showUntrackedFiles no
```

## Install Erlang / Elixir / NodeJS

      asdf plugin add erlang
      asdf plugin add elixir
      asdf plugin add nodejs
      asdf install erlang 24.3.4
      asdf global erlang 24.3.4
      asdf reshim erlang
      asdf install elixir 1.13
      asdf global elixir 1.13
      asdf reshim elixir
      asdf install nodejs 16.15.1
      asdf global nodejs 16.15.1
      asdf reshim nodejs

